Estimated number of people in the labor force (18 years and older) who&nbsp;are unemployed,&nbsp;<span>divided by the total labor force; expressed as percent.</span></p>
<p>Individuals are classified as unemployed and in the labor force if they do not have a job, have actively looked for work in the prior 4 weeks, and are currently available for work.</p>
